the study and collaboration (sac) room is a communal space that is available during the academic year for currently registered lurie college students and is located in sweeney hall 446. the space provides access to a computer, printer, and copy machine. technical assistance is available by appointment at 408-924-3640. students must use their sjsu tower cards to access the room. the sac room is managed by the lurie college student success center . contact them at luriecollege-successcenter@sjsu.edu or at 408-924-2700 for assistance. sjsu connie l. lurie college of education sweeney hall 103 one washington square san jose, ca 95192-0071 create opportunities for lurie college students! 